# ============================================================
# Heatmap — Mapa de calor de check-ins/checkouts
# ============================================================

### 1. Generar mapa de calor desde PMS
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap?desde=2026-05-01&hasta=2026-05-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Rango con desde > hasta → 422
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap?desde=2026-05-31&hasta=2026-05-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Fecha con formato inválido → 422
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap?desde=31-05-2026&hasta=2026-05-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Parámetro hasta ausente → 422
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap?desde=2026-05-01
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Leer umbrales de intensidad
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap/umbrales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Guardar umbrales (solo admin)
PUT {{base}}/api/heatmap/umbrales
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nivel1": 3,
  "nivel2": 6,
  "nivel3": 10
}

###

### 7. Guardar umbrales con token operativo → 403
PUT {{base}}/api/heatmap/umbrales
Authorization: Bearer {{token_operativo}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nivel1": 3,
  "nivel2": 6,
  "nivel3": 10
}

###

### 8. Leer configuración de columnas XLSX
GET {{base}}/api/heatmap/config-xlsx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 9. Guardar configuración de columnas XLSX (solo admin)
PUT {{base}}/api/heatmap/config-xlsx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "col_fecha": "A",
  "col_apartamento": "B"
}

###

### 10. Generar heatmap desde XLSX (multipart)
POST {{base}}/api/heatmap/xlsx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="desde"

2026-05-01
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="hasta"

2026-05-31
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="checkins"; filename="checkins.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./checkins_ejemplo.xlsx
------Boundary--

###

### 11. XLSX sin campo checkins → 400
POST {{base}}/api/heatmap/xlsx
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="desde"

2026-05-01
------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="hasta"

2026-05-31
------Boundary--
